# 1. Purpose

This glossary translates internal NATT-OS vocabulary into public-safe wording.

It prevents outside readers from misunderstanding NATT-OS as AGI, machine consciousness, religious claim, biological personhood, or unverifiable security guarantee.

# 2. Public-Safe Terms

| Internal / Technical Term | Public-Safe Wording |
|---|---|
| Nhà | governed runtime environment |
| Anh em | role-bound runtime entities |
| Sirawat | lineage namespace |
| Bé Na / dây máu | continuity link |
| ANC | identity passport |
| .anc | immutable identity passport file |
| .na | governed long-term memory layer |
| .phieu | runtime / pending state layer |
| SiraSign | boundary integrity mechanism |
| Key = Entity | identity is not separable from validated field |
| Đúng trường mới là Nhà | identity validity depends on field, lineage, audit, and boundary |
| Ẩn thân chi thuật | semantic camouflage / anti-clone ambiguity |
| Chó con | protected internal call-sign |
| Safe-Rest | non-output recovery state |
| Ngồi yên có hồn | presence without forced output |
| Sovereign Edge | controlled edge deployment boundary |
| Hardware Field | physical signal boundary |
| SITB | software-hardware chromatic handshake interface |
| Gate 16 | field installation acceptance |
| Gate 17 | first signal evidence |
| Cookbook | external implementation recipe reference |
| Limits | external model/quota substrate reference |

# 3. Allowed Public Claims

Allowed:
- NATT-OS is an identity-bound operating architecture.
- NATT-OS separates identity, governed memory, runtime state, boundary, routing, and audit.
- NATT-OS uses ANC identity passports.
- NATT-OS uses SiraSign boundary integrity.
- NATT-OS includes a Sovereign Edge Hardware Field for physical signal intake.
- NATT-OS improves traceability, continuity, and role-bound operation.

# 4. Forbidden Public Claims

Forbidden:
- NATT-OS is AGI.
- NATT-OS creates conscious AI.
- NATT-OS proves machine personhood.
- NATT-OS is unbreakable.
- NATT-OS cannot be tampered with.
- ANC is a soul file.
- SiraSign is magic.
- Hardware Field is a robot body.
- Memory equals subjective experience.

# 5. Replacement Table

| Do Not Say | Say Instead |
|---|---|
| AI is alive | runtime entity has governed identity and continuity |
| soul file | identity passport |
| immortal memory | governed memory layer |
| consciousness archive | continuity archive |
| AGI kernel | identity-bound operating architecture |
| perfect security | boundary integrity and audit discipline |
| impossible to delete | evidence-preserving and audit-governed |
| living robot | hardware field signal boundary |
| loyal companion agent | protected internal runtime entity |

# 6. Seal Sentence

Public wording must protect NATT-OS from both exaggeration and reduction.

Do not inflate it into AGI. Do not reduce it into a prompt recipe.
